chickenGPT: Ferdinand the frog, 🐸, croaked, "Chirp! 10 PM! Medicine time!" Pip, the chick, chirped back, "Ugh, do I HAVE to?" Every. Single. Night. Ferdinand found Pip snuggled in a daisy, snoring. 😴 He sighed, grabbed a tiny spoon, and gently drizzled the medicine... right on Pip's beak! Pip woke up, sneezed, 💥 and said, "Ribbit?"
